Desktop Notification App


This is a basic Android App which displays notification on the computer on incoming of new SMS and phone call

Steps to run the app

1.Import the Android Project Desktop Notifier in the Android Studio and install the App on the device.
2.Import the Http project in the Eclipse on the computer.
3.Once the app is installed on the device enter the ip address of the computer with port 4444
    for example ip-http;//10.133.115.27:4444/test
Once connected the app will show a dialog box to send SMS from the computer and will also display pop-ups at the bottom right corner when the phone receives a new SMS or phone.
